::Magmatron::

    "I have you at a disposition hmm...well that could be useful." Magmatron 
said to the Cat. "Since I already had plans for you that Bobertron 
interrupted I will go ahead with them now that Bobertron is gone. You are you 
find any Maximals and become one of them, now go." Magmatron said waving his 
hand. The doors opened so Cheetor could run out.
    "Yes, this should prove very different indeed." Magmatron said as he 
turned to go to his Quarters.
